The '''Jal Shey Mentor''' was the highest rank of the [[Jal Shey]] order, and the equivalent of the [[Jedi Master/Legends|Master]] in the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]]. They were highly respected for their wisdom and understanding of [[The Force/Legends|the Force]], and were considered to be the brightest minds in the known galaxy.

